<plot>It's 2374. Laia, Olivia and Ji Lan are three sisters who log in the Virtual Room, a private 3D chat where they can talk and live all kind of adventures. Laia is sporty and aggressive, although she's rather clumsy and not very good with boys. Olívia is apparently shallow but she's much more astute than she seems. She always uses her brains for evil purposes, though, Laia being her most usual victim. Ji Lan is smart and calm and spends quite a good amount of time trying to stop her sisters from fighting.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?524966</url></doc>
